title: Oberon media - Hidden Jewel Adventure - New Hidden Object, Match
description:
Embark on a mesmerizing journey across a magical land, solving puzzles along the way. Complete the final challenge and discover the mystery of the hidden power jewel in this enchanting mix of match-3 and hidden object gameplay.
Unlimited, unrestricted gameplay.
Journey across a magical land.
Unlock and complete bonus mini games.
Enjoy colorful, full-screen graphics.
Win achievement trophies.
SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:

Operating system: Windows XP,Vista
Processor speed: 1 GHz or faster
RAM: 512MB
Hard drive space (uncompressed): 19MB
Graphics Card: 32MB or better
1024x768 or higher screen resolution
